      "text": [
        "658 - وَ فِي رِوَايَةِ مُعَاوِيَةَ بْنِ عَمَّارٍ: «وَقْتُ اَلْعِشَاءِ اَلْآخِرَةِ إِلَى ثُلُثِ اَللَّيْلِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.658 - In the narration of Muawiya ibn Ammar it is stated:\n\"The time for the last Isha prayer extends until one-third of the night”."
        ]
      }
    }
